      "description": "Three-loop planar vertex integral family with nine propagators and three ISPs, arising in $\\mathcal{O}(\\alpha^2 \\alpha_s)$ corrections to Z-pole electroweak precision observables. Contains two massive W-boson propagators and one massive top-quark propagator. External momenta $p_1, p_2$ are massless ($p_1^2=p_2^2=0$) with $p=p_1+p_2$ and $p^2=M_Z^2$. Evaluated using DE transport from Euclidean boundary to Minkowski point, yielding 8+ digits precision for integrals up to tensor rank 3. The family involves 77 master integrals.",
